# EquiPulse AI Cursor Rules
# Used to configure custom styling rules and enforce high-contrast CSS mappings.

* Always use Tailwind CSS utility classes.
* Enforce high-contrast accessibility (WCAG 2.1 AA) when generating components.
* Prioritize Framer Motion for gesture-based swipe controls.
* Use localized components (i18n aware) instead of hardcoded strings.
* Maintain strict TypeScript boundaries for all components and API handlers.
* For visual charts, do NOT pull in heavy libraries (like Chart.js). Use inline SVGs styled with Tailwind CSS to ensure 100/100 PageSpeed scores.
